# Feature Implementation Guidelines

## Core Features

### Memory Gallery
- Implement grid and list views for memory display
- Support filtering by tags
- Include smooth transitions between memory items
- Allow for memory creation, editing, and deletion

### Community
- Implement AI chat interface with message bubbles
- Create community post listing with engagement metrics
- Support topic filtering and search

### Proposal Planning
- Build interactive proposal creation wizard
- Implement proposal template gallery
- Include form validation for user inputs

### Profile
- Display user statistics with animated counters
- Implement settings management
- Show activity timeline with appropriate icons

## Implementation Approach
- Start with UI components before adding functionality
- Create mock data services before implementing real APIs
- Test on multiple screen sizes during development
- Implement error handling for all network operations